					<div class="leftnote"><span class="xar-sub">Posted Jan 31, 2010 at 8:30:43 PM</span></div>
										<div style="float: left;"><strong class="xar-sub">Subject: kid needs help with writing
</strong></div>
					<div style="clear: both;"></div>
				</div>
				<div>
															<p>well he's like in 5th grade and he tells me that he worries about failing because he's still having a hard time writing summaries for his social studies class.  And also has problems with writing an answer to questions that say explain this (based on story).  I'm starting to think he has adhd because i asked him if after he reads the story if he remembers it or what happened and he said not really.  I just want to figure out some way to make it easier for him, thanks</p>
									</div>
							</td>
		</tr><tr>
