			<td class="xar-norm message">
				<div class="xarbb-messagecontrols">
					<div class="leftnote"><span class="xar-sub">Posted:Feb 01, 2010 5:13:56 PM</span></div>
					<div class="rightnote">
											</div>
					<div style="float:left;"><strong class="xar-sub">Subject:<a name="89928" href="http://www.ldonline.org/xarbb/topic/15612#89928">kid needs help with writing
</a></strong></div>
					<div style="clear: both;"></div>
				</div>
				<div style="clear: left;">
															<p>So do you think the difficulty is related to comprehension and not to written expression?  Has he been evaluated for a learning disability through the school? </p>
<p>If you decide to allow the school to evaluate -- make sure that you make your request in writing.  </p>
<p>If he is identified with an LD, you may want to consider membership of either of the following:</p>
<p><a href="http://www.rfbf.org" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">www.rfbf.org</a><br />
<a href="http://www.bookshare.org" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">www.bookshare.org</a></p>
<p>Best wishes.</p>
																				</div>
			</td>
